reviewText: mavelous darling... christopher guest in some of his funniest moments on snl. i don't know many people who can stretch their characters like him
I loved every minute of this. This is among the funniest stuff ever made and easily the best of Saturday Night Live.

I find the videos to be a little dated, but there are still a few classic parodies that I love.  The hard part in getting this is, in some cases, without knowing the original ad the parody isn't quite as funny.

If you remember the early SNL skits (Like the Buddwesier Ice Hockey ad with Robin Williams and Joe Piscopo... my favorite) and want to remember some of them ... this is the tape for you.

I you are just looking for something funny and aren't familiar with the older SNL skits ... I would look for something else.
